high_descs: walk to the side of the table, turn right to the stove
grab the pan on the stove
turn right, walk to the counter by the sink
put the pan on the counter

put the tomato in the pan
anns.task_desc: move the pan from the stove to the counter, put the tomato in the pan

high_descs: Walk to the table then turn right and walk to the table in front of you then take a couple steps left to stand in front of the stove.
Pick up the pan that's on the stoves front left burner.
Turn around and walk to the table then turn left and walk to the counter that's in front of you.
Put the pan to the left of the tomato so the pan side is close to the wall with the handle pointing down.
Put the tomato in the pan.
anns.task_desc: Put a tomato in a pan that's on the counter.

high_descs: Walk towards the stove on your right.
Pick up the black pan on the stove.
Turn right and head towards the counter to the left of the sink.
Place the pan to the left of the tomato on the counter.
Pick up the tomato from the counter.
Place the tomato in the pan.
anns.task_desc: Place a tomato in the black pan.
